  "rationale": "<p>Setting the two expressions for y equal: x² − 3 = x + 3, so x² − x − 6 = 0, which factors as (x − 3)(x + 2) = 0. With x &gt; 0, x = 3. Then y = 3 + 3 = 6. The solution is (3, 6).</p>",
